               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of Mary, መልክአ፡ ማርያም፡; Image of Jesus Christ, መልክአ፡  ኢየሱስ፡; Image of Arägawi/Zä-Mika'el, መልክዐ፡ አረጋዊ፡ /ዘሚካኤል፡;  Image of Gäbrä Mänfäs Qəddus, መልክአ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡; Image of Michael, መልክአ፡ ሚካኤል፡; Image of Gabriel, መልክአ፡ ገብርኤል፡; Image of Saint George, መልክአ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from = "3r" to = "15v"/><title type = "complete" ref="LIT4112Salam"/></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from = "15v" to = "30r"/><title type = "complete" ref="LIT4131Salam"/></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from = "30r" to = "37v"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2998RepCh278"/>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ እምግብጽ፡ ፍኖተ፡ ግዕዛን፡ ዘመርሖ። ለእግረ፡ እስራኤል፡ ሞቅሆ። እማዕሠረ፡ ቅኔ፡ ዘተፈትሖ።
                    </incipit>
                    </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from = "27v" to = "42r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2915RepCh196"/></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from = "42r" to = "52v"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1860Malkea"/></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6"><locus from = "52v" to = "59v"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1849Malkea"/></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7"><locus from = "59v" to = "60v"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2866RepCh147"/>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ዘሰሌዳ፡ ሞገስ፡ መጽሐፉ። ዘያሜኒ፡ ኵሎ፡ ወያስተሴፉ። ጥዑመ፡ ዜና፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ለሐሊብ፡ እጐልት፡ ሱታፉ።
                    </incipit>
                    </msItem>

